Author: ICOHunt
Title: announcement
Body: Can you give an estimated distribution of tokens between public and team? Thanks  "5. KARB Tokens Retained by Team and Founders The Team will keep the difference between the amount of KARB Tokens created and amount distributed during the KARB Token distribution, plus the incentive, which will be no less than 5% (the “Retained KARB”). The Team intends to provide some portion of the Retained KARB to team members. The Team may decide to sell some or all of any additional Retained KARB although there are no plans to do this at the moment."
